1.title: Gladigator
1.plot: Alligators are decimating a South Texas wallaby ranch! Buck and his companions, Mitch and Ryder, must relocate the gators before any more wallabies are lost. Buck attempts to remove a skunk from a rancher's hog trailer. It's a stinky situation!

2.title: Hogway to Hell
2.plot: A woman finds that her ex-boyfriend has planted four wild hogs into her mobile home and it's up to Buck to evict them. Buck attempts to locate a diseased nilgai antelope before it spreads the fatal illness to a South Texas rancher's livestock.

3.title: Chopper Throwdown
3.plot: Buck recruits his entire crew for an epic helicopter and net gun mission to return an escaped stud bull elk back to the breeder. Then, Buck, Mitch and Ryder attempt to catch a sneaky armadillo that's been damaging the foundation of a retirement home.

4.title: Buckin' Bobcat
4.plot: Buck, Mitch and Ryder help a South Texas sheep rancher catch his escaped breeding ram before it falls victim to predators. A bobcat is killing a farmer's goats. Buck, Mitch and Ryder deploy tracking dogs in an attempt to find the elusive cat.

5.title: Barracuda Battle
5.plot: An underwater engineer needs protection from aggressive barracudas and enlists expert spear fisherman and scuba diver Buck Medley to be his barracuda bodyguard. Buck investigates a strange gremlin living inside wife Margret Ann's friend's house.

6.title: Buzz Kill
6.plot: Buck is out with his wife Margret Ann when a friend calls with a crisis - a gator is trapped inside his garage! Buck races off to help with Margret Ann in tow. Buck, Mitch and Ryder face angry bees that may just be the feared Africanized killer bees!

7.title: Killer Coyote
7.plot: Buck's friend Tim needs three wild hogs removed from his cattle ranch. Short-handed, Buck enlists Tim's green ranch hand Kennan to help. Then, a rogue coyote is killing calves on Tim's ranch. It's up to Buck and Kennan to restore the balance of life!

8.title: Chainsaw on Hooves
8.plot: An aggressive javelina is trapped in a woman's backyard. Buck and his hired help, Mitch and Ryder, must find a way to force the animal back to nature. When a family friend finds a poisonous snake in a pool, Buck must enter the water to catch it.

imdb.plot outline: Whether it's a rogue coyote killing calves, alligators decimating a wallaby ranch, or a stinky situation with a skunk in a hog trailer, Texans call on Buck Medley. A problem-solver specializing in relocating animals and known for his unusual tactics, Buck will re-locate wild bulls that cross into Mexico, rescue baby chicks from a snake, and attempt to tame a group of angry bees.
